OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FPSNI Chief Constable Jon Boutcher has
OL,8,Fsaid he has "significant concerns"
OL,9,Fover the force's capacity to deal with
OL,10,Fviolence against women and girls.
OL,12,FMr Boutcher told MPs there is
OL,13,Fcurrently an acceptance in society of
OL,14,Fmisogyny which he has never seen
OL,15,Fbefore.
OL,17,FHe was asked during an appearance
OL,18,Fbefore the Northern Ireland Affairs
OL,19,FCommittee about concerns around the
OL,20,Flevels of violence against women in
OL,21,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
