OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FAt the weekend, police launched a
OL,8,Fmurder investigation after young
OL,9,Fmother Amy Doherty was killed in
OL,10,FLondonderry.
OL,12,FA man has been arrested.
OL,14,FOn Monday, Stephen McCullagh was
OL,15,Fconvicted at Belfast Crown Court of
OL,16,Fthe murder of his pregnant partner
OL,17,FNatalie McNally in Lurgan in December
OL,18,F2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FCommittee chairwoman Tonia Antoniazzi
OL,8,Fsaid 30 women had died violently in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland since 2020.
OL,11,FShe added: "Statistics show it is
OL,12,Fworse in Northern Ireland."How do you
OL,13,Fdeal with the fact that it is worse in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland and how does your
OL,15,Fforce address male violence against
OL,16,Fwomen and girls?"
OL,26,@sD@LOUtD@[OUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FMr Boutcher passed on his condolences
OL,8,Fto the family of Ms Doherty. He said
OL,9,Fhe had also met with the family of
OL,10,FChloe Mitchell, who was killed in Co
OL,11,FAntrim in 2023, and had spoken this
OL,12,Fweek to the lead investigating officer
OL,13,Fin the McNally case.
OL,15,FHe said: "I want to assure this
OL,16,Fcommittee we are taking a number of
OL,17,Fsteps, that violence against women and
OL,18,Fgirls is a significant priority for
OL,19,Fthe Police Service of Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,F"I do want to make one point though.
OL,8,FOften it is mentioned that violence
OL,9,Fagainst women and girls is more
OL,10,Fsignificant in Northern Ireland than
OL,11,Felsewhere.
OL,13,F"I think that is possibly because in
OL,14,F2019 the BBC published an article
OL,15,Fusing figures from Eurostat,
OL,16,Fhighlighting the number of homicides
OL,17,Fin Northern Ireland as being
OL,18,Fcomparable to Romania and at the very
OL,19,Fhigh end of femicides in Europe.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,F"The data given was 0.43% per 100,000
OL,8,Fpopulation, which is the same as
OL,9,FRomania.
OL,11,F"It quoted eight murders and the data
OL,12,Fwas a single year, 2017."The data was
OL,13,Fwrong. There were four murders that
OL,14,Fyear, three against women and one
OL,15,Fdomestic murder against a male.
OL,17,F"The rate for Northern Ireland on that
OL,18,Fdata would have put us just below
OL,19,FEngland and Wales and just above
OL,20,FSwitzerland, in the middle of the
OL,21,Ftable of European countries."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUtD@YOUyD@AOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FMr Boutcher said he had looked at the
OL,8,Fdata from 2012 to 2023, "which puts us
OL,9,Fright in the middle of the data set
OL,10,Ffor Europe".
OL,12,FThe Chief Constable then referred to
OL,13,Fthe death of showjumper Katie Simpson
OL,14,Fin 2020.
OL,16,FPolice originally thought she had died
OL,17,Fby suicide, but the following year
OL,18,FJonathan Creswell, the partner of Ms
OL,19,FSimpson's sister, was arrested on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,26,@pD@YOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FThe trial of Creswell, 36, for murder
OL,8,Fended in April last year after his
OL,9,Fsudden death.
OL,11,FMr Boutcher said: "I don't know if
OL,12,Fthis is Northern Ireland specific or I
OL,13,Fam of a generation now because of what
OL,14,Fis happening online or because of the
OL,15,Fvile nature of things like Andrew Tate
OL,16,Fand what he seems to do with young men
OL,17,Fand boys and trying to groom them as
OL,18,Fto how they behave, which is abhorrent.
OL,26,@sD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,F"But there seems to be an acceptance
OL,8,Faround misogyny the like of which I
OL,9,Fhave not seen.
OL,11,F"We have got to draw a line and say
OL,12,Fthis is unacceptable."
OL,14,FHe said lots of work is done by the
OL,15,FPSNI, including commissioning review
OL,16,Fof how the force is dealing with
OL,17,Fincidents of violence against women.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUtD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
