CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FHe said: "We have done a cultural
OL,8,Faudit in the last 12 months
OL,9,Fspecifically looking at behaviours
OL,10,Fwithin the organisation, focusing on
OL,11,Fensuring that we are doing everything
OL,12,Fwe possibly can to deal with any
OL,13,Fabhorrent behaviours, whether that is
OL,14,Fmisogyny or any sort of hatefulness
OL,15,Fwithin the organisation towards
OL,16,Fcolleagues."
OL,18,FSDLP leader Claire Hanna said she did
OL,19,Fnot think people "wanted to quibble on
OL,20,Fnumbers".
OL,26,@oD@JOUxD@LO]{D@ROU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
