PN,44511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FShe added: "I think Ellie Flanagan and
OL,8,FAmy Doherty became the 29th and 20th
OL,9,Fwomen killed since 2020 and comparable
OL,10,Ffigures for England show we do have a
OL,11,Ffemicide rate that is almost twice of
OL,12,Fthe island next door and certainly of
OL,13,Fthe south."
OL,15,FShe asked if the PSNI had the proper
OL,16,Fresources to bring perpetrators to
OL,17,Fjustice.
OL,26,@oD@LOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
