PN,44512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FMr Boutcher said: "For me violence
OL,8,Fagainst women and girls is one of my
OL,9,Fbiggest concerns with regards to my
OL,10,Frole as the chief constable of
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland, that is why we are
OL,12,Fprioritising.
OL,14,F"With regards to our ability to deal
OL,15,Fwith these sorts of cases, where there
OL,16,Fis such life-changing harm to
OL,17,Findividuals, I am significantly
OL,18,Fconcerned about our capacity."
OL,26,@oD@SOUvD@AOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
