PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774534302
OL,3,CPSNI chief raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccapacity to deal with violence against
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FHe referenced the case of Alexander
OL,8,FMcCartney, a prolific online abuser
OL,9,Ffrom Newry who was jailed in 20 years
OL,10,Fin 2024 for the online sexual abuse of
OL,11,Fchildren and the manslaughter of a 12-
OL,12,Fyear-old girl.
OL,14,FMr Boutcher said the Police Ombudsman
OL,15,Fhad reported the force did not have
OL,16,F"sufficient resources" to tackle those
OL,17,Fkinds of cases.
